sourcesContent:
import { screenSizes, colors } from '../../constants'

styles = {
  navbar: {
    position: 'fixed',
    height: '4rem',
    width: '100%',
    backgroundColor: colors[1].slateGrey,
    zIndex: 1001,
    paddingLeft: '1rem',
    paddingRight: '1rem',
    marginLeft: 'auto',
    marginRight: 'auto',
    maxWidth: `${screenSizes.screenLg}px`
  },
  navbarContent: {
    position: 'relative',
    display: 'flex',
    flexDirection: 'row',
    height: '100%'
  }
}
